      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta fajuttibs wiſſi Kohki\nwiŗs Lauka/ ka es tas KUŅGS/\nto augstu Kohku efmu paſemmo-\njie/ to ſemmu Kohku pa-augſti-\nnajs/ to ſattu Kohku kaltejs/ un\nto kaltufchu Kohku darrijs eeſek-\ntam. Es tas KUŅGS efmuto\nrunnajs/ un darriſchu to.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta XVIII. Nodalla.\nCzekiêls aprahi rohs Judus taſalkama Wahr-\nda pehz fo tee walcajſchi/ un jazziſchi: Tee\nTehwi irr fapuuſchus Wiha Rekkarus ehdu-\nſchi/ un teem Behrneem irr tee Sohbi ap-\nmisejſchi : 1. Un ka Deewß netweenu kahta\nZitta Noseeguma deht ſohdus/ bet ikwee-\nnam buhs fawn paſchm Noseegumu neſt : 4\nJo winnam ue patiſk ta Nahwe ta/ kas\nmirſt: 23/ 32.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tkat notikke ta KUŅ-\nGA Wahrdß us man/\nkas fazzija:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "( Kas jums fait? ) ka\njuhs icho faſkamo Wahrdnu wal-\nkajat no Israêta Semmes/ un\nfakkat : Tee Tehwi irr fapuu-\nſchus Wiha Rekkarus ehduſchi/\nun teem Behrneem irr tee Soh-\nbi apmiseiſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tik teescham ka es dſihwo-\nju/ ſakka tas KUngs KUŅGS:\nTas ne notiks wairs ſtarp jums/\nka tchis ſakkins Wahrdß eeſch\nIsraêta taps walkahts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Redsi / wiſſas Dwehſeles\nman peederr/ itt ka ta Tehwa\nDwehſele/ ta arridsan ta Dehla\nDwehteſe man peederr. Kurra\nwehſele apgrehkojahs / ta no-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kav nu tas taſtis irr/\ndarra kaſ Teesa un Taſniba ir\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kaß uß Kalneem ne eh-\nnu jawas Azzis ne vazett uß\nIsraêta Namna Suhdu-De-\nweem/ nedß fawa Tuwaka Se-\nwn apgabna/ un pee ween-\nfahrnainas Geewas ne gull.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kas netweenu noſpaid-\nun dohd tam Paradneekam f\nwu Rihlu atpakkaſ/ kas neuer\nar Warru laupa/ un dohd ta-\nIſfalkuſcham Maiſi/ un a-\ngehrbj to Plikku ar Drebb-hin\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kaß Augumi ne dſen-\nnedß Pagaidus plebſch/ fan-\nRohku no Netaifnibas nogreefe-\nun nefß pateefu Teesu ſarp wa-\nnu un ohtru.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kaß mannôs Likkomôß sta-\nga/ un mannas Teetaß farg-\npeetizzigat turredamces/ tas pa-\nTaifns dſihwohs/ ſakka t-\nKungß KUŅGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet ja tas irr ween-\nDehlu dſemdinajs/ kas Bahrla-\nſitajs irr/ kas Affinis iſleij/ k-\nfawam Brabtam wcenu\nſchihm Leetahu padarra.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kas wiſſas ſchihs Le-\ntas ne darra/ bet ehd arridſ-\nus Kalneem/ un apgabna fan-\nTuwaka Geewu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kaß to Nabbagu\nWaijadſigu noſpaida / tau-\ndauds Laupiſchanas / ne atdo-\nto Rihlu/ un vazett fawas D-\nzis us teem Sahou-Deewe-\ndarra Negantbu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Isdohd us Augumi/\npleb-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
